OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772139893
OL,3,CFresh appeal for information about
OL,4,Ccouple killed in car bomb
OL,6,FA fresh appeal for information has
OL,7,Fbeen made over the killing of a former
OL,8,Fpolice officer and his wife by a car
OL,9,Fbomb in 1990.
OL,11,FJames Sefton, 65, and his wife Ellen,
OL,12,F66, were killed when a booby trap
OL,13,Fdevice exploded under their car in
OL,14,FBelfast.
OL,16,FIt happened on Wednesday June 6 after
OL,17,Fthe couple had left their home on
OL,18,FLyndhurst Gardens and driven towards
OL,19,FBelfast city centre.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
