OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772139893
OL,3,CFresh appeal for information about
OL,4,Ccouple killed in car bomb
OL,6,FAt approximately 10am, as they passed
OL,7,Fthe old Forth River Primary School on
OL,8,FBallygomartin Road, the bomb exploded
OL,9,Fbeneath their car.
OL,11,FMr Sefton, who was driving, was
OL,12,Ffatally injured and died in the Mater
OL,13,FHospital.
OL,15,FMrs Sefton was critically injured and
OL,16,Ftransferred to the Royal Victoria
OL,17,FHospital. She died the following day.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
