OL,3,CFresh appeal for information about
OL,4,Ccouple killed in car bomb
OL,6,FThe new appeal for information has
OL,7,Fbeen made by the Independent
OL,8,FCommission for Reconciliation and
OL,9,FInformation Recovery (ICRIR) which is
OL,10,Fprobing the murders at the request of
OL,11,Fthe Sefton family.
OL,13,FAssistant commissioner Amanda Logan,
OL,14,Fwho is leading the commission's
OL,15,Finvestigations team, said the family
OL,16,Fis seeking the truth around what
OL,17,Fhappened.
OL,19,FShe said even the smallest detail
OL,20,Fcould help.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
