PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772139893
OL,3,CFresh appeal for information about
OL,4,Ccouple killed in car bomb
OL,6,F"It's over 35 years since James and
OL,7,FEllen were killed," she said.
OL,9,F"Their family is seeking the truth
OL,10,Fabout what happened and we believe
OL,11,Fthere is someone out there who may
OL,12,Fhold the vital piece of information
OL,13,Fthat could make a difference to the
OL,14,Finvestigation.
OL,16,F"Even the smallest detail could help
OL,17,Fus understand what happened and why."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@SO]qD@AOUxD@AOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
