PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772139893
OL,3,CFresh appeal for information about
OL,4,Ccouple killed in car bomb
OL,6,FMs Logan added that the suffering of
OL,7,Fthe Sefton family was "representative
OL,8,Fof the pain of so many victims,
OL,9,Fsurvivors and families".
OL,11,F"People are still suffering, deprived
OL,12,Fof information and with no
OL,13,Faccountability," she said.
OL,15,F"Our job at the commission is to try
OL,16,Fto deliver answers for people who have
OL,17,Fbeen searching for them for decades."
OL,26,@oD@WOUqD@WO]sD@AOUuD@PO]wD@AOUyD@eO]
